@freethechi has initiated a new endeavor that will hopefully draw attention to the countless CHIs sitting in high kill shelters and help them get noticed or at a minimum buy them time while they are being networked by the wonderful rescue community. We intruduce Lily, the first recipient of the @freethechi bandana. Repost @northcentralshelter. Say hello to sweet, little Lily!
Lily is an adorable, 8 pounds, 8 years old girl who is quite nervous in the shelter, but will be your adoring friend in exchange for treats and belly rubs. We believe she will thrive in a home that can help build her confidence and work on leash training. She seems to perk up when dogs are around and has been kenneled with other small dogs and done well.
Lily has been waiting at the shelter since Sept. 17, 2017 when she was surrendered with 3 other dogs (#A1729507 4 yrs old, female Chihuahua also still available).
She wants a home where she can cuddle in a warm bed, watch Netflix, eat all the treats, and chill! Not too much to ask for this little doe. Please share or come give Lily a home in time for the holidays!

This sweet golden-eyed girl is Josie, and she is up for any kind of Friday fun, and any other day. At about 8 months old and 34 lbs, she is a petite Chocolate Labrador Retriever mix. She was found roaming the streets of Houston in terrible condition with Demodex mange. She was able to go to a foster home where with medication, good food and loving care she has grown a beautiful chocolate-colored coat and blossomed into a super sweet dog. She is fully vetted, spayed and micro-chipped. She's been living in the foster home for 8 weeks now and has learned how to be a member of a family. She is crate trained, house trained and walks perfectly on leash. Josie loves all dogs big and small, all people, kids included. She's just a total love bug that never stops wiggling and wagging her tail. She's the happiest girl! She also knows the commands 'Sit' and 'Stay.' Josie loves to play with toys, play fetch in the yard and go for walks. Everyone that meets her falls madly in love with her and her sweet personality. If you'd like to meet this special puppy, contact: forgottenpetadvocates@yahoo.com
